    "chapter": "9. Pharmacologic Approaches to Glycemic Treatment",
    "section": "9.9",
    "recommendation_id": "9.9a",
    "text": "Metformin dose should be reduced when eGFR falls below 45 mL/min/1.73 m² and discontinued when eGFR falls below 30 mL/min/1.73 m².",
